57
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:02,670
Weiyang,

58
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,550
come with me.

59
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:05,750
I'll take you away from the capital.

60
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,620
