124
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:39,850
If the Fifth Prince's mansion can't contain him,

125
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:41,310
I'll send him to the Court of Judicial Review.

126
00:06:41,330 --> 00:06:42,659
