136
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,260
Let her go!

137
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:04,350
Let her go!

138
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,720
Ye Beichen!

139
00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:08,130
Let go!

140
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:16,360
Shame on you!

141
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,530
