142
00:07:21,610 --> 00:07:22,540
-Weiyang.
-You-

143
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:23,890
Let me go!

144
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,160
-Let me go! Let me go!
-Let me go!

145
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,030
Ye Beichen!

146
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:33,010
[Jinxiu Cloth Shop]

147
00:07:26,230 --> 00:07:28,010
Let me go, Ye Beichen!

148
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:30,180
In broad daylight,

149
