166
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:04,230
♫I point to the moon, questioning beneath it, before the city tower♫

167
00:08:01,110 --> 00:08:01,910
Yes.

168
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:02,890
Ye Beichen.

169
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:04,080
