170
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,790
You met your lover in secret.

171
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,510
♫She's in red♫

172
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:08,430
♫With angry eyes, a word severs grudges♫

173
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:07,290
