250
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,690
I don't care about all that.

251
00:12:24,070 --> 00:12:24,950
Anyway,

252
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:26,430
I will never let go of your hand

253
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:27,700
